contentrichtext.text: '''Zabel''' may refer to: *[[:de:Albert_Zabel|Albert Heinrich Zabel]], German harpist and composer *[[Erik Zabel]], a German professional road bicycle racer *[[Jim Zabel]], an American sports broadcaster *[[Joe Zabel]] *[[Mark Zabel]] *[[Steve Zabel]] *[[Zip Zabel]] *[[Lord Raptor]] (Zabel Zarock), a character from the ''Darkstalkers'' video game series *[[Zabel, Bulgaria|Zabel]], a village in [[Tran, Bulgaria]] *[[Terbinafine]]; Zabel is a generic version of the drug Terbinafine sold in Australia *[[Zabel (engine)]], a German two-stroke motocross engine {{disambig}}
